<section class="section aerys-solution" id="solution" aria-labelledby="solution-title">
  <div class="container">

    <span class="sec-label">The Mechanism</span>
    <h2 id="solution-title" class="aerys-solution__headline">
      Close your mouth while you sleep.<br>
      <span class="hi">Your body handles everything else.</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="aerys-solution__opener">That&rsquo;s the entire solution.</p>

    <p class="aerys-solution__body">Not a device. Not a prescription. Not a regimen that requires you to change twelve things at once. One intervention, applied in one second, that gives your body the one condition it needs to repair itself: uninterrupted nasal breathing through the night.</p>

    <!-- Mechanism video -->
    <div class="aerys-solution__video-wrap" aria-label="See how AERYS™ works">
      <video
        class="aerys-solution__video"
        autoplay
        muted
        loop
        playsinline
        preload="metadata"
        poster="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0808/8112/3545/files/product-main.png?v=1776730988"
      >
        <source src="https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/3ab1485f227a4c9bbcb94e018a71103a.mp4" type="video/mp4">
      </video>
    </div>

    <div class="aerys-solution__chain" role="list" aria-label="How AERYS works">
      <div class="aerys-solution__step" role="listitem">
        <div class="aerys-solution__step-num">Step 01</div>
        <div class="aerys-solution__step-title">Lip Seal</div>
        <p class="aerys-solution__step-desc">The strip seals your lips gently and completely. No restriction. No discomfort. If your mouth needs to open, it opens.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aerys-solution__step" role="listitem">
        <div class="aerys-solution__step-num">Step 02</div>
        <div class="aerys-solution__step-title">Nasal Breathing</div>
        <p class="aerys-solution__step-desc">Your body switches to nasal breathing. Nitric oxide production increases, dilating blood vessels and improving oxygen delivery.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aerys-solution__step" role="listitem">
        <div class="aerys-solution__step-num">Step 03</div>
        <div class="aerys-solution__step-title">O&#8322; Uptake</div>
        <p class="aerys-solution__step-desc">Oxygen efficiency increases up to 30%. Your heart rate slows. Your nervous system stops registering threat signals.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aerys-solution__step" role="listitem">
        <div class="aerys-solution__step-num">Step 04</div>
        <div class="aerys-solution__step-title">Deep REM</div>
        <p class="aerys-solution__step-desc">Your sleep cycles deepen and stabilize. You move through REM without interruption. In the morning, your jaw is relaxed. Your mouth is not dry.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="aerys-solution__note">This works because the material is different. AERYS™ uses a pharmaceutical-grade silicone adhesive &mdash; the same classification used in clinical wound dressings and dermatological patches. It creates a secure seal that holds through six, seven, eight hours of sleep without shifting. It peels off clean in the morning, leaving no residue, no inflammation, no evidence it was there.</p>

    <p class="aerys-solution__note">It works on beards. It works on sensitive skin. It works on the seventh night and the one hundred and seventh night the same way it worked on the first.</p>

    <div class="aerys-solution__rhythm" aria-label="AERYS summary">
      <span>One strip.</span>
      <span>One second.</span>
      <span>Your body does the rest.</span>
    </div>

    <a href="#bundles" class="btn btn-dark">Start Sleeping Better Tonight &rarr;</a>

  </div>
</section>

